why would a tank 1v1 a class made to out sustain and out damage him. u dont see {{champion:57}} winning a fight against {{champion:420}} {{champion:164}} like no that's not what's gonna happen. if you're on equal terms you need another bruiser like {{champion:75}} {{champion:150}} to fight him, and if he's ahead you need to bring your ADC. Later in the game he's most likely going to splitpush, which you either have to go equal with or just kill him by bringing like 3 people when there's no threat of objectives the enemy can get. If he decides not to splitpush, he is kitable and will be pretty useless as long as you have some damage threats. 

>Because that would be stupid and not the fact it takes the combined effort of several champs to actually kill him while the Darius still has a team of his own.

